widgets_values: Set length with frame count. Make sure motion video is long enough.

Play with these values to change the brightness of either the masked or unmasked area. It will effect how much it will be de-noised or not. 

Min of 0 means it will look completely like original input.
Right click, and choose "Open in Mask Editor" to draw a mask of areas you want animated more.
